==成立==
Mozilla公司成立於2005年8月3日，負責處理Mozilla基金會[[營業額|收益]]的相關業務。作為非營利性組織，Mozilla基金會在收益類型和金額方面受到限制。Mozilla公司作為一個應稅組織（本質上是商業運作），不必遵守這樣嚴格的規定。Mozilla公司成立後，接手了Mozilla基金會的幾個領域，包括協調和整合Firefox和Thunderbird（由全球[[自由軟體運動|自由軟件社區]]開發）以及與[[企業|企業]]關係的管理。

隨著Mozilla公司的成立，Mozilla基金會的其他成員將精力集中在Mozilla專案的治理和政策問題上。2005年11月，隨著Mozilla Firefox 1.5的發布，Mozilla公司的mozilla.com網站被公佈為Firefox和Thunderbird線上產品的新家。

在2006年，Mozilla公司創造了6680萬美元的收入和1980萬美元的支出，其中85％的收入來自「將Google指定為瀏覽器的預設搜尋引擎以及搜尋結果頁面投放的廣告<ref>{{cite web |last=Keizer |first=Gregg |date=October 25, 2007 |title=Mozilla can live without Google's money, Baker says |work=Computerworld |url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/2539499/networking/mozilla-can-live-without-google-s-money--baker-says.html |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2017年11月12日 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112190744/https://www.computerworld.com/article/2539499/networking/mozilla-can-live-without-google-s-money--baker-says.html |accessdate=2017年11月12日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Houston |first=Thomas |work=The Verge |date=December 5, 2011 |accessdate=December 6, 2011 |title=Future of Firefox's Google search partnership remains uncertain |url=https://www.theverge.com/2011/12/5/2612918/future-of-firefoxs-google-search-partnership-remains-uncertain |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804035146/https://www.theverge.com/2011/12/5/2612918/future-of-firefoxs-google-search-partnership-remains-uncertain |dead-url=no }}</ref>」。

==著名事件==
2006年3月，{{link-en|賈森·卡拉卡尼斯|Jason Calacanis}}在他的部落格上報導說，Mozilla公司在去年獲得了7200萬美元，主要得益於Firefox瀏覽器中的[[Google|Google]]搜尋列<ref>Calacanis blog: [http://www.calacanis.com/2006/03/06/firefox-mozilla-corporation-mozilla-foundation-made-72m-last/ "Firefox (Mozilla Corporation/Mozilla Foundation) made $72M last year?!"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.calacanis.com/2006/03/06/firefox-mozilla-corporation-mozilla-foundation-made-72m-last/ |date=20200929192612 }}</ref>。隨後，當時的董事會成員[[克里斯多佛·布里扎德|克里斯多佛·布里扎德]]在他的部落格上寫道：「我不會披露真正的收入數字，這個數字是不正確的。<ref>{{cite web|work=0xDeadBeef.com|url=http://www.0xdeadbeef.com/weblog/2006/03/apply-pinky-to-corner-of-mouth/|title=apply pinky to corner of mouth|first=Christopher|last=Blizzard|date=March 7, 2006|accessdate=June 1, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120716183229/http://www.0xdeadbeef.com/weblog/2006/03/apply-pinky-to-corner-of-mouth/|archivedate=2012年7月16日}}</ref>」兩年後，[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]寫道：「為了將Google設置為Firefox的預設搜尋引擎，Google向Mozilla支付了大筆費用──2006年，總額達到了5700萬美元，占公司總收入的85％。這項交易最初將在2006年到期，但後來延長到2008年，現在將延續到2011年。<ref>{{cite news|first=Jason|last=Kincaid|work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|url=https://techcrunch.com/2008/08/28/mozilla-extends-lucrative-deal-with-google-for-3-years/|title=Mozilla Extends Lucrative Deal With Google For 3 Years|date=August 28, 2008|accessdate=June 1, 2012|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921064331/https://techcrunch.com/2008/08/28/mozilla-extends-lucrative-deal-with-google-for-3-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」這筆交易再次延長了三年，直到2014年11月。根據協議，Mozilla將從Google獲得另外的9億美元（每年3億美元），將近前一筆金額的三倍<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2398046,00.asp|title=Google Paying Mozilla Almost $1B for Firefox Search: Why?|first=David|last=Murphy|date=December 24, 2011|accessdate=June 1, 2012|work=PC Magazine|archive-date=2018-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718105312/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2398046,00.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2006年8月，[[微軟|微軟]]邀請Mozilla開發人員進行合作，以確保Mozilla軟體與當時即將推出的Windows Vista的相容性<ref>{{cite web|work=[[Google_Groups|Google Groups]]|url=http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.planning/browse_frm/thread/622906b52581628e/a303e61ccb5c8149#a303e61ccb5c8149|title=mozilla.dev.planning Microsoft offer|accessdate=2017-11-11|archive-date=2013-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613042039/http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.planning/browse_frm/thread/622906b52581628e/a303e61ccb5c8149#a303e61ccb5c8149|dead-url=no}}</ref>。微軟將在位於華盛頓州雷蒙德市的總部提供一對一會議。Mozilla接受了這個提議<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.com/Microsoft+offers+helping+hand+to+Firefox/2100-1032_3-6109455.html | title=Microsoft offers helping hand to Firefox | work=[[CNET|CNET]] | date=August 24, 2006 | author=Baker, Colin | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120717223839/http://news.cnet.com/Microsoft-offers-helping-hand-to-Firefox/2100-1032_3-6109455.html | archivedate=2012年7月17日 | deadurl=yes | accessdate=2017年11月11日 }}</ref>。

2014年3月，Mozilla在任命[[布蘭登·艾克|布蘭登·艾克]]擔任新任首席執行長（CEO）之後受到了一些批評。2008年，艾克捐款1000美元，支持[[加利福尼亞州8號提案|加利福尼亞州8號提案]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Silver |first=Nate |url=http://www.fivethirtyeight.com/datalab/how-rare-are-anti-gay-marriage-donations-in-silicon-valley/ |title=How Rare Are Anti-Gay-Marriage Donations in Silicon Valley? |publisher=FiveThirtyEight |date=2014-04-04 |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170503210859/https://fivethirtyeight.com/datalab/how-rare-are-anti-gay-marriage-donations-in-silicon-valley/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這是一項禁止法律承認[[加州同性婚姻|加州同性婚姻]]的投票<ref>{{cite web | url=https://arstechnica.com/business/2014/03/gay-firefox-developers-boycott-mozilla-to-protest-ceo-hire/ | title=Gay Firefox developers boycott Mozilla to protest CEO hire [Updated] | publisher=ArsTechnica | date=March 25, 2014 | accessdate=April 1, 2014 | author=Machkovech, Sam | archive-date=2017-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313174311/https://arstechnica.com/business/2014/03/gay-firefox-developers-boycott-mozilla-to-protest-ceo-hire/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。據報導，六名Mozilla董事會成員中有三人辭職<ref name="Resign">{{cite news | url=https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/03/28/three-mozilla-board-members-resign-over-choice-of-new-ceo/ | title=Three Mozilla Board Members Resign over Choice of New CEO | work=Wall Street Journal | date=March 28, 2014 | accessdate=April 1, 2014 | author=Barr, Alistair | archive-date=2018-10-07 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20181007223214/https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/03/28/three-mozilla-board-members-resign-over-choice-of-new-ceo/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，儘管Mozilla表示辭職的董事會成員有「各種各樣的原因」<ref>{{cite web | url=https://arstechnica.com/business/2014/03/three-mozilla-board-members-including-two-former-ceos-step-down/ | title=Three Mozilla board members—including former CEOs—step down | work=ArsTechnica | date=March 29, 2014 | accessdate=April 2, 2014 | author=Machkovech, Sam | archive-date=2020-05-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523030033/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2014/03/three-mozilla-board-members-including-two-former-ceos-step-down/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並重申其繼續致力於LGBT平等<ref>{{cite web | url=https://blog.mozilla.org/press/2014/03/mozilla-statement-on-diversity/ | title=Mozilla Statement on Diversity | publisher=Mozilla | work=Official blog | date=March 25, 2014 | accessdate=April 1, 2014 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034017/https://blog.mozilla.org/press/2014/03/mozilla-statement-on-diversity/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://brendaneich.com/2014/03/inclusiveness-at-mozilla/ | title=Inclusiveness at Mozilla | work=Personal blog | date=March 26, 2014 | accessdate=April 1, 2014 | author=Eich, Brendan | archive-date=2020-11-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118091231/https://brendaneich.com/2014/03/inclusiveness-at-mozilla/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括同性婚姻<ref>{{cite web | url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/03/29/mozilla-supports-lgbt-equality/ | title=Mozilla Supports LGBT Equality | publisher=Mozilla | work=Official blog | date=March 29, 2014 | accessdate=April 2, 2014 | archive-date=2020-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123221654/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/03/29/mozilla-supports-lgbt-equality/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月1日，線上交友網站OkCupid開始向[[Mozilla_Firefox|Mozilla Firefox]]使用者展示一條訊息，敦促他們改用其他網頁瀏覽器，指出OkCupid網站上的8％的配對是同性伴侶<ref>{{cite web | url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/31/tech/web/firefox-okcupid-protest/ | title=OkCupid protests Firefox over CEO's anti-same-sex marriage donation | publisher=CNN | date=April 1, 2014 | accessdate=April 1, 2014 | author=Kelly, Heather | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031608/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/31/tech/web/firefox-okcupid-protest | dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月3日，Mozilla宣布艾克決定辭去首席執行長職務，離開Mozilla基金會董事會<ref>{{cite web |author=David Robertson |url=http://www.christiantoday.com/article/firefox.fails.the.tolerance.test.were.free.but.it.may.cost.us.our.jobs/36600.htm |title=Firefox fails the tolerance test: We're free but it may cost us our jobs | Christian News on Christian Today |website=Christiantoday.com |date=2014-04-06 |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112131900/https://www.christiantoday.com/article/firefox.fails.the.tolerance.test.were.free.but.it.may.cost.us.our.jobs/36600.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Eich-resign">{{cite web|url=http://recode.net/2014/04/03/mozilla-co-founder-brendan-eich-resigns-as-ceo-and-also-from-foundation-board/|title=Mozilla Co-Founder Brendan Eich Resigns as CEO, Leaves Foundation Board|last=Swisher|first=Kara|date=April 3, 2014|publisher=Re/code|accessdate=April 3, 2014|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420170449/http://recode.net/2014/04/03/mozilla-co-founder-brendan-eich-resigns-as-ceo-and-also-from-foundation-board/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月，Mozilla前首席行銷長[[克里斯·比爾德|克里斯·比爾德]]被任命為臨時首席執行長。比爾德於同年7月28日被任命為首席執行長.<ref name="chris ceo">{{cite web | url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/07/28/chris-beard-named-ceo-of-mozilla/ | title=Chris Beard Named CEO of Mozilla | work=Mozilla | date=July 28, 2014 | accessdate=July 28, 2014 | author=Mitchell Baker | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015502/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/07/28/chris-beard-named-ceo-of-mozilla/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年2月27日，Mozilla收購網路儲存服務[[Pocket|Pocket]]<ref name="verge-mozacquisition">{{cite web|title=Mozilla acquires Pocket to gain a foothold on mobile devices|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/2/27/14752590/mozilla-acquires-pocket-read-it-later|website=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=27 February 2017|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030822/https://www.theverge.com/2017/2/27/14752590/mozilla-acquires-pocket-read-it-later|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

